    <!--  Main Fragments -->
    <string name="PettPlantFragment"><![CDATA[<p><u>Entrainment Mode</u>: To start a brain wave
        entrainment cycle, select the desired sequence from the Entrainment Mode drop down list and
        tap the Run button to begin. Tap the Stop button to stop the current entrainment cycle and
        return the cycle to the beginning. Tap the Pause button if you wish to pause the current
        cycle and resume from that same point later.</p>
        <p><u>Color Mode</u>: To select the color pattern that your PETT will display, select one
        from the Color Mode drop down list. Use the Speed slider to adjust the rate at which the
        colors change. The Hold button will freeze the colors at any given point. Tap the Hold
        button again to resume the animation.</p>
        <p><u>Hint</u>: The brain wave entrainment mode will run with any color pattern you
        select. For the best results in maximizing the stroboscopic effect, we recommend choosing
        one of the first 3 Rainbow cycle presets that turn all of the LEDs on full bright, and
        placing your PETT in a fully darkened room.</p>
        <p>Enjoy!</p>]]></string>

